divs: Sighting DetailsOn march 13th ,I was on the 10t fl of the fallsview casino hotel.My window faced the american falls.So with my camera at full 4x zoom i took some pics in the direction above goat island.When i got home and uploaded the pics to my computer i found these 4 like objects-saucer-like objects in one photo.The first is the original photo,the i tried to bring out some high- lights and added some warm filters to the photo. I dont think this is some out of foucus bird or insect--notice the light reflect from the middle of all the objects...
